Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.84,0:00:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.81,0:00:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在...你在哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.31,0:00:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本...坂本！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.41,0:00:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.41,0:00:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他丟下我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.71,0:00:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.41,0:00:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.26,0:00:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傷者就得置身事外嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.93,0:00:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.69,0:00:31.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被丟開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.34,0:00:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都不告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.57,0:00:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:37.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芯片的事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是不得已 我也不是想瞞著你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.81,0:00:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在做我的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.81,0:00:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本你不也是...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相互競爭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.01,0:00:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞞著我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先下手為強
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.59,0:00:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,先下手為強...！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.41,0:00:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有6枚芯片了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.81,0:00:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰都信不過
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這些芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是隨手撿的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.21,0:00:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但只是我想拿來做保險
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.73,0:01:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣不行 好想回去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.41,0:01:04.68,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣會死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:05.46,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.46,0:01:06.54,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,不想死...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見你...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見你啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.76,0:01:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.09,0:01:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是...是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.67,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,誰...誰在那裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.34,0:01:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回來了嗎 坂本？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 剛才那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.99,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於也出現幻覺...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.22,0:01:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.13,0:01:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.24,0:01:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.88,0:01:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底什麼時候到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.47,0:02:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想...見你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.92,0:02:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.72,0:02:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼說我也沒辦法啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.72,0:02:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.35,0:02:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.02,0:02:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 爸爸 我受了重傷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.43,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 芯片還沒有收齊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.71,0:02:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家想見爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.72,0:02:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想見你啊 這還用說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.76,0:02:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 芯片...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.71,0:02:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八枚芯片...還沒拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒這回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.37,0:02:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爸 你已經呆到連數都數不清了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說...數？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在又幾枚芯片？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,芯 芯片有...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.05,0:03:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 二...三
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可不夠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.96,0:03:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 還...有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.08,0:03:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四 五 六
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.78,0:03:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七 八！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回 回 回得去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 柚彥 昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.78,0:03:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸會回去的 會回去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.96,0:03:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後一起去吃大餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到味乃家去吃大吃特吃煎餅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,染成赤紅的指南針
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷的映入眼眶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.21,0:04:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I defy the beating of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深陷死亡的亢奮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.58,0:04:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,充滿矛盾的痛楚 彷彿在確認生命的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.39,0:04:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I m left tolick my wounds again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.88,0:04:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,REAL 漸漸解開
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.21,0:04:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷見到孤獨中的人影
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲的夢destroy my existence now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在 在四散碎裂的世界之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捨棄束搏自己的枷鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沉溺與這種誘惑 disillusion delusion
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,曾幾 何時失落的鮮明的歲月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也在忘卻一切的瞬間 resolution redemption
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.33,0:04:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天也要將戰鬥握在手中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so take hold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.14,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just watch a new world as it will unfold
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:05:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dont go of your vision
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.42,0:05:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just take life head on and find your reason
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起霧了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且太陽也基本下山了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巨蜥們就要醒來 快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.56,0:05:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噓 好像能聽到...什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是巨蜥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.36,0:05:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 這聲音...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.39,0:05:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是追蹤式炸彈！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.26,0:06:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.00,0:06:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我被鎖定了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.67,0:06:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 進入其爆範圍的話就會爆炸的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追蹤式炸彈...擁有這種炸彈的是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.61,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！ 如果是你 請你住手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是同伴嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 後面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.63,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 還在起爆範圍內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.91,0:06:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.83,0:06:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 腳...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.90,0:07:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 好過分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生 求求你 快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.36,0:07:13.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這麼過分的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要做這種事 為什麼..
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.59,0:07:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集齊6枚芯片的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個人就將要受到考驗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道平先生是集齊了芯片 所以就背叛了我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有反應
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟藏在什麼地方 那個老狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼背叛我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好了一起離開的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.47,0:08:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.86,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總免不了產生你會不會不回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.67,0:08:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會不會拋棄我了的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.94,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滿腦子都是這些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要 不要不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次真的撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是你現在拋下我 我...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.49,0:08:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我會崩潰的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了給平先生療傷 也需要乾淨的毛巾和水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 我們會拿到很多好吃的回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.72,0:08:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果平先生有這麼做的理由 那就是我讓他感到不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他明明那麼害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻為什麼沒有發覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.61,0:08:53.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就好像我 像我在不知不覺中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.05,0:08:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了和老爸一樣的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老爸是個工作狂 對我不理不睬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.88,0:09:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老媽自作主張離婚 又自作主張帶來了繼父
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.89,0:09:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大人都很自私 事事只考慮自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝出一副很喜歡我的樣子 然後自我滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.86,0:09:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直這麼認為
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我卻把己所不欲加與平先生了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.35,0:09:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忽視了平先生的心情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.26,0:09:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.85,0:09:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是這樣逃避現實的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.16,0:09:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 龍太!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,振作一點 炸彈的聲音又傳來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,動作快 得從這兒逃走才行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃 卑彌呼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我們現在玩遊戲和BTOOOM規則相同
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼遙控式炸彈應該也和網絡裡的性能一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就不能猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能猶豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.87,0:10:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.27,0:10:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有被鎖定的目標進入起爆氛圍才會爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來保護 龍太由我來保護
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這...難道是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.48,0:10:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼就是我在BTOOOM裡面遇到的那個卑彌呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:18.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生沒有移動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他一定藏在能看到我們的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.26,0:11:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 遙控式炸彈只能鎖定一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.75,0:11:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坂本 卑彌呼 你們別怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是遊戲 我也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 是這樣吧 柚彥 昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.33,0:11:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.98,0:12:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽得到 在那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.83,0:12:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來幾次都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.69,0:12:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像 有點不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.03,0:12:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是想殺我 怎麼會用這麼單純的攻擊手法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對 他不會這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.66,0:12:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一手大有來頭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是這樣 那顆炸彈的目標是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.46,0:12:26.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生的目標是...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.02,0:12:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼 是你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.88,0:12:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 料中了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被 被看穿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟 糟糕 糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這 這下慘了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.31,0:12:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.44,0:13:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.99,0:13:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再做這種事了 請回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.74,0:13:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 我的腰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.13,0:13:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,會被殺的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就剩下...一個了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.43,0:13:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被殺之前 先殺了他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了柚彥 為了昭子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生 我想向你道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想和你一起回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.80,0:14:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和平先生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會再讓你感到不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次我會好好幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.58,0:14:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你 再給我一次機會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 平先生 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我向你道歉吧 平先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阪 阪本
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 我 我...我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.04,0:14:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是所謂因果報應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.17,0:14:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是對我所做過的事的懲罰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不住了 阪本 卑彌呼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想回家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.93,0:15:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是 想見家人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.19,0:15:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,柚彥 昭子 對不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸好痛苦 已經受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.07,0:15:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平 平...先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是要一起回去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:46.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來啊 說句話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像往常那樣說個無聊的笑話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.00,0:15:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杯麵泡兩分鐘就吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:16:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都 還沒向 平先生道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.95,0:16:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.51,0:16:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生 是不是一開始就打算背叛我們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像伊達先生那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 平先生不是那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他只是個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.71,0:16:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正因為是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.79,0:16:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會吃驚 才會懷疑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都愛惜自己的生命 都想早點回家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 受了重傷被一個人丟下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.89,0:16:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被絕望逼得走投無路的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.95,0:16:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生的心就崩潰了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.60,0:16:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像是我 就像是我殺的一樣 是我...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 你也想回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 真想立刻就逃離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,逃離這種屎一樣的地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以回去的 龍太
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.53,0:17:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以...回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 這是剛才回收的芯片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.52,0:17:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一枚是平先生的 另兩枚是平先生悄悄收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這三枚和我們所收集的加一起就有六枚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我還有一枚 龍太也有一枚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣有權離開島的八枚芯片就齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們之中有一個人死去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,另一個人就能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.77,0:17:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 殺了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.02,0:18:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有歸宿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.82,0:18:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你改變了無處可去的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.36,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們在現實中明明並無交集
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻有種心靈相通的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即便是在虛擬的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.68,0:18:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也拯救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.48,0:18:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而在來到這個島上之後
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.94,0:18:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無數次命懸一線 即將崩潰的時候也是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.38,0:18:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我清楚的明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.55,0:18:34.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太是我活下去的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 如果龍太能得救
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.39,0:18:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我無論變成什麼樣 無論會怎麼樣都...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開 開什麼玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我有那麼想回去 甚至不惜犧牲你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.83,0:18:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是那種人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會拋棄你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本不可能拋棄你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.55,0:19:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論是現實中 還是在虛擬世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.32,0:19:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼 你就是那個卑彌呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.19,0:19:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我總算發覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.43,0:19:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總算見到你了 卑彌呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.48,0:19:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直 一直很想見你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.99,0:20:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 她現在也還是很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.46,0:20:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻為了我 拚命地忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.45,0:20:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是上嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.59,0:20:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我應該告訴過你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.51,0:20:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有行動才會取勝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.25,0:20:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出男子氣概來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.05,0:20:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是你又要束博自己 然後自我滿足？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.74,0:20:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 你一輩子也別想超過我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.35,0:21:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！ 我已經不再...憧景你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我終於明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.92,0:21:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最重要的是珍惜他人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.27,0:21:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我能明白這點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:21.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平先生就不會死了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也能好好地面對家人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.16,0:21:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以為只有自己是特別的 自以為是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧不起別人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.15,0:21:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.20,0:21:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就壓根不會被帶到這個島上來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.94,0:21:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,織田 我和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.07,0:21:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會變成像你那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別賴在我的心裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.74,0:22:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太？怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.34,0:22:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 突然推倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.86,0:22:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在這種地方順勢...總覺得 不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.89,0:22:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卑彌呼 一起離開這個島吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.89,0:22:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.00,0:22:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等我們回去...等我們回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.97,0:22:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就正式向你提出交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對 這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.75,0:22:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要回去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.99,0:22:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和卑彌呼一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.97,0:22:46.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離開這個地域
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.60,0:22:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,24小時 說什麼都要在24小時之內修復
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.90,0:23:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到了島上後  盡快的展開修復！明白了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.17,0:23:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白 那我們走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.38,0:23:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這件事絕對不能讓客戶知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.51,0:23:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.39,0:23:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽的 島上的設備居然偏偏在這重要的時候故障
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.30,0:23:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,靠 到底怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,龍太 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.67,0:23:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能做到的就只有這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.74,0:22:34.36,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,最果ての{\fs60}STORY{\r}抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.51,0:22:38.24,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,あてもなく{\fs60}彷徨い{\r}続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.67,0:22:40.92,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,滲{\r}んだ new world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.09,0:22:44.03,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,The game has only just begun
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.16,0:22:46.44,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,終焉{\r}のEYES
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.33,0:22:49.67,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where tomorrow brings a new game
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.67,0:22:52.54,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to learn that pain is gain ready {\fs60}FIGHT
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.61,0:23:04.99,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,過去の失望{\fs60}塗{\r}りつぶすために
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:07.64,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,犠牲{\r}にしてきた未来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.76,0:23:09.64,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,ライフ\N僕の{\fs60}命{\r}が尽きるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.85,0:23:12.72,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,その定めぶち{\fs60}壊{\r}していくのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.03,0:23:16.69,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,嗚呼 Break out and start a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.69,0:23:21.93,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,一つの答えを{\fs60}探{\r}して
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.24,0:23:25.01,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,限界の{\fs60}RACE{\r}に挑んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.01,0:23:27.54,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,一度切りのチャンスと{\fs60}知{\r}って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.42,0:23:31.92,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,背負った{\fs60}運命{\r}越えていくんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:35.03,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,最果ての{\fs60}STORY{\r}抱いて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.18,0:23:39.19,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,あてもなく{\fs60}彷徨い{\r}続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.43,0:23:42.02,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,滲{\r}んだ new world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:44.43,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,The game has only just begun
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.92,0:23:49.97,Staff,,0000,0000,0000,,今{\fs60}終焉{\r}のEYES
